summary: Ambitious, resilient, and communicative student, ready to take on challenges and develop further in academic and social aspects. A young chemist coming from Belgrade, Serbia. My passion for chemistry started very early on, and I have nurtured it through many national and international competitions and through working on various research projects. My interests lie in the fields of organic synthesis and supramolecular chemistry. I am  currently doing a master's degree programme at the Technical University of Eindhoven.
